#id=1
#text=Since it 's Spring now , I decided that my yard needed another tree in it .
#id=2
#text=I walked around the yard for a while deciding where I wanted to put it .
#id=3
#text=Once I picked the spot out , I got online and looked up what kinds of trees grow best in my area .
#id=4
#text=I decided on a nice pine tree and headed to the nursery .
#id=5
#text=I took a little time looking at their pine trees until I found the one I liked .
#id=6
#text=I bought it and some topsoil to plant it in and got them loaded into my car .
#id=7
#text=Once I was home , I grabbed my shovel and went out to the place I wanted to put the tree .
#id=8
#text=I started digging and kept at it until I had a hole deep and wide enough to fit the little tree in .
#id=9
#text=I put it in the hole and filled around it with the nice topsoil I bought so I had good dirt to start growing in .
#text=I spread out the dirt I had taken out of the hole so I did n't have a pile of dirt , then watered the tree and put my tools away .
#text=I knwo it will take years , but that tree is going to look great once it ; s bigger .
